{
  "texts": [
    "We included the 310 most recently published cases in this study.",
    "Ten cases were excluded because they either did not provide a definitive final diagnosis or exceeded the maximum context length of the GPT-4 API.",
    "A full list of all cases included (by title and DOI number) can be found in Supplementary Data 2.",
    "For this evaluation, we compared traditional CoT prompting to the highest performing clinical reasoning CoT prompt (differential diagnosis reasoning) on the modified MedQA dataset.",
    "One traditional CoT prompt and four clinical reasoning prompts were developed (differential diagnosis, analytical, Bayesian and intuitive reasoning)."
  ]
}